{"tid":340243,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"固執既人好撚可惡","createTime":"2017-07-29T17:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T20:10:45.000Z","uid":66951,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80f3d63e182fb3b8c676e1a7c060f3ed34e1e511","tid":340243,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"我發現固執真係數一數二仆街既性格<br />\n<br />\n階級觀念更加係助長左固執既人<br />\n<br />\n而通常男性係固執過女人 好自以為是<br />\n<br />\n平時話廢老 多數講緊公園D呀伯 又話自己食鹽多過食米 仇視青年人 但其實自己根本一無是處（有料到就唔使臨老仲係公園9up啦）<br />\n<br />\n一個家族入面 愈老既人愈固執 恃住D濕鳩輩分係壓住後輩 因為自尊心太重 衰唔起 所以點都好 都要堅持自己係岩既 人地係錯既 （可能係現實生活太霉 只可以靠老在家族中搵返些少自尊）<br />\n<br />\n同固執既人相處 就好似圍繞住同一件事不停轉圈 浪費心機時間 而無任何收穫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d984c47d2369fec3a4571aedd0edfbfaa7ea479","tid":340243,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:02:18.000Z","msg":"唔知開邊個台，但睇黎開感情台錯了，又唔係男歡女愛"},{"pid":"0943aa2d3fd62a4ae52b10dc8674b61f48b67a47","tid":340243,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb89e56981ea56fd76ce5d9d8218e1a1a489ba0","tid":340243,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n固執既人好可惡 你同意嗎"},{"pid":"4c849c51510fb7de867f30ed98043c965e9ea2fa","tid":340243,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n固執既人好可惡 你同意嗎</blockquote><br />\n講完又唔撚聽"},{"pid":"e4be6880f423c6203a8e0ba88ba6cedde1714338","tid":340243,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n固執既人好可惡 你同意嗎</blockquote><br />\n講完又唔撚聽</blockquote><br />\n唔明"},{"pid":"25ee287203c83d8f943c03eda5695cf016fa3d3c","tid":340243,"uid":86403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n固執既人好可惡 你同意嗎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚同意，同佢地講野好撚哂時間。<br />\n日日都圍住為同一個on9問題而煩惱，仲要燥埋其他人，講完又唔聽，堅持為自己個on9煩惱轉圈，成世就咁，變左無野改善過"},{"pid":"e16339516cc9d781b121440501beccc00f5670e2","tid":340243,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n固執既人好可惡 你同意嗎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚同意，同佢地講野好撚哂時間。<br />\n日日都圍住為同一個on9問題而煩惱，仲要燥埋其他人，講完又唔聽，堅持為自己個on9煩惱轉圈，成世就咁，變左無野改善過</blockquote><br />\n為一個問題煩惱未算最on9<br />\n<br />\n將自己價值觀/諗法強行殖入他人身上先係on9"},{"pid":"1ad6e66df49be204141be327e2b5c5d89d293e9d","tid":340243,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:20:01.000Z","msg":"推到天光"},{"pid":"2682dfd2efaeb9c785b36888882dc3b9f19eb266","tid":340243,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:30:31.000Z","msg":"話我假膠 可以睇下我上面真心說話<br />\n<br />\n無賭錢既人會講得出上面既野嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1773a4263038577f3ef8091c61233abfbe86912a","tid":340243,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:39:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話我假膠 可以睇下我上面真心說話<br />\n<br />\n無賭錢既人會講得出上面既野嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n回錯"},{"pid":"c0b5fecdd9b853d42f6f7b1f8458da3abb7bdc8c","tid":340243,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20